                        "description":  "Choose either the caster plus up to eight willing visible creatures within 10 feet or one visible Large-or-smaller object that is not held or carried by an unwilling creature, then choose a known destination on the same plane. Destination familiarity drives the d100 outcome table: Permanent Circle and Linked Object arrive on target, while Very Familiar, Seen Casually, Viewed Once or Described, and False Destination rows can produce Mishap, Similar Area, Off Target, or On Target results.",
